<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Hack Club | AI</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #ffffff;
        --text: #111;
        --muted: #555;
        --red: #ec3750;
        --code-bg: #f5f5f5;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --bg: #0a0a0a;
          --text: #f9f9f9;
          --muted: #aaa;
          --red: #ff5c77;
          --code-bg: #1a1a1a;
        }
      }

      body {
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
      }

      header {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      h1 {
        color: var(--red);
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      h2, h3 {
        color: var(--red);
        font-family: monospace;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--red);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      code {
        font-family: monospace;
        background: var(--code-bg);
        padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }

      pre {
        background: var(--code-bg);
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        font-family: monospace;
      }

      section {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .note {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>ai.hackclub.com</h1>
      <p>
        An experimental service providing unlimited
        <code>/chat/completions</code> for free, for teens in
        <a href="https://hackclub.com/" target="_blank">Hack Club</a>. No API key needed.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>{{ total_tokens }}</strong> tokens processed since January 2025. Current model:
        <strong><code>{{ model }}</code></strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Open source at
        <a href="https://github.com/hackclub/ai" target="_blank">github.com/hackclub/ai</a>!
      </p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Usage</h2>

      <h3>Chat Completions</h3>
      <pre><code>curl -X POST https://ai.hackclub.com/chat/completions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Tell me a joke!"}]
}'</code></pre>

      <h3>Get Current Model</h3>
      <p>To get current model:</p>
      <pre><code>curl https://ai.hackclub.com/model</code></pre>
      <p>Example response: <code>{{ model }}</code></p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Terms</h2>
      <p>
        You must be a teenager in the <a href="https://hackclub.com/slack">Hack Club Slack</a>.
        All requests and responses are logged to prevent abuse. Projects only – no personal use.
        This means you can't use it in Cursor or anything similar for the moment!
      </p>
      <p class="note">
        Abuse means this will get shut down – we're a nonprofit funded by donations.
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
